msgstr "Estableix els paràmetres a passar al full d'estil."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Ús"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"La manera més habitual d'executar <command>meinproc6</command> és simplement "
"com <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>fitxer-docbook</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> a on <replaceable>fitxer-docbook</replaceable> generalment "
"serà index.docbook. Aquesta ordre crea pàgines &HTML; del fitxer DocBook. "
"Cal tenir en compte que aquestes pàgines només són visibles en els "
"navegadors basats en el &kde; (com el &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Si necessiteu veure la sortida &HTML; en un altre navegador (per exemple, si "
"el feu disponible en línia), utilitzeu <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>nom-full-"
"estil</replaceable> <replaceable>fitxer-docbook</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> a on <replaceable>nom-full-estil</replaceable> serà el camí "
"complet cap a un dels fulls d'estil XSL en &lt;"
"prefix_instal·lació_kdoctools&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. Per a "
"generar una sortida adequada per a la web, podeu utilitzar <command>kde-web."
"xsl</command> o <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. Per a més detalls, "
"vegeu el fitxer <filename>README</filename> en aquesta carpeta."

